    <h1>WHAT TO SEE</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201114/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-11-14"><time>2020-11-14</time></a>
        - <span>LIFE</span>
